  "text": [
    "How must it be",
    "to be moss,",
    "that slipcover of rocks?\u2014",
    "imagine,",
    "greening in the dark,",
    "longing for north,",
    "the silence",
    "of birds gone south.",
    "How does moss do it,",
    "all day",
    "in a dank place",
    "and never a cough?\u2014",
    "a wet dust",
    "where light fails,",
    "where the chisel",
    "cut the name."
  ],
  "title": "Moss",
  "year": ""
